# [TSVWG](../wg/tsvwg.html)

## Summary

This interim TSVWG meeting focused on the progress and technical considerations for two main work items: DTLS for SCTP and UDP Options. For DTLS for SCTP, two primary approaches were discussed in detail, along with liaison feedback from 3GPP and IPR considerations. A design team was proposed to further refine requirements and security analysis for this work. For UDP Options, an update on the resolution of GitHub issues was provided, indicating readiness for a final Working Group Last Call.

## Key Discussion Points

